  "DescIdentified": {
    "type": "cexolocstring",
    "value": {
      "0": "This wand allows you to:\n1) Record and Playback up to 63 different phrases\n2) Throw your voice to a place or an object (using a character prefix)\n3) Mute NPCs\n\nIf you target yourself:\n-Record Mode (record a phrase... make sure you are visible and an NPC is nearby)\n-Mute All NPCs (Toggle)\n-Ditto Mode (creates a voice)\n\nIf you are targeting a creature:\n- Playback mode (the creature speaks a pre-recorded phrase)\n- Mute this NPC (Toggle)\n- Ditto Mode (the NPC will repeat what you say prefixed by a colon)\n\nIf you are targeting nothing:\n- Loiter Mode (creates a voice that will wait until a PC gets near, and then say a pre-recorded phrase. They will destroy themselves in the process)\n- Turn On/Off DM Spy (Toggle)\n- Ditto Mode\n\nBy Hahnsoo (hahns_shin@hotmail.com)"
    }
